Comment: 0,0:21:57.08,0:23:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,你想怎麼死？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,我先這麼追過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.16,Main,,0,0,0,,打倒你為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:32.65,Main_Up,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,明里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,不行 武偵是不能殺人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,快讓我見識見識鷹捲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,夾竹桃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:40.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\3a&HFF&\fs120\fnA-OTF Outai Kaisho Std Light\1c&HFFFFFF&\shad6\pos(576,747)}11彈
